ItemDisplay[NMAG SOCK>0]: %NAME% %RED%[%WHITE%%SOCKETS%%RED%]
ItemDisplay[!NMAG SOCK>0]: %NAME% %RED%[%WHITE%%SOCKETS%%RED%]

